 class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3830690/extras/8e9926121452379332790db90ebe7965.avif?t=1776391686\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3830690/extras_big/8e9926121452379332790db90ebe7965.webp?t=1776391686 width=1560 height=877 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本作為成人向模擬遊戲，包含角色培育、日常互動、以及可選擇觸發的親密場景，描繪出一段在逃亡與共處中誕生的浪漫喜劇故事。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >【✦遊戲核心：冒險、生活、與她的日常✦】</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3830690/extras/f47fa8bdee82253a1a6718265a4fcbf3.avif?t=1776391686\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3830690/extras_big/f47fa8bdee82253a1a6718265a4fcbf3.webp?t=1776391686 width=1560 height=877 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >【箱庭培育】：待在屬於二人的秘密基地，從溫馨餐桌到私密床鋪，一步步拉近彼此的心。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3830690/extras/4576fc5590164829b7f2a8de76e47f00.avif?t=1776391686\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3830690/extras_big/4576fc5590164829b7f2a8de76e47f00.webp?t=1776391686 width=1560 height=877 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >【資源蒐集】：肚子餓了就出外採集，結晶不夠就狩獵魔物。為了生存，更為了變得更「強」。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3830690/extras/0d09522ddec0dc04ef49a7cc8f597275.avif?t=1776391686\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3830690/extras_big/0d09522ddec0dc04ef49a7cc8f597275.webp?t=1776391686 width=1560 height=877 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >【回合制策略】：經典且直覺的戰鬥系統，看著莉潔特在戰場上展現颯爽英姿！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3830690/extras/0a1c9c58345f1f90d29210e4f6958e7c.avif?t=1776391686\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3830690/extras_big/0a1c9c58345f1f90d29210e4f6958e7c.webp?t=1776391686 width=1560 height=877 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >【極致放鬆】：修行累了嗎？回到休息室享受多樣化的「互動模式」，讓壓力在喘息聲中徹底釋放。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3830690/extras/2c399f321bedd23099a97516e95362c8.avif?t=1776391686\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3830690/extras_big/2c399f321bedd23099a97516e95362c8.webp?t=1776391686 width=1560 height=877 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >【✦頂級感官饗宴：帶給你最深刻的沉浸體驗✦】</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✨ 女性角色們全完整日文語音！強化角色魅力與沉浸感～</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✨ 全3D卡通渲染風格，臨場感加好加滿！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✨ 支援360度視角互動場景，深入感受角色動態與細節✨</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✨ 超過29組動畫演出之親密場景♥</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✨ 共有3種結局！根據選擇改變你們的未來吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3830690/extras/d040a3f165eb32149811acabd28b2009.avif?t=1776391686\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3830690/extras_big/d040a3f165eb32149811acabd28b2009.webp?t=1776391686 width=1560 height=877 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >【✦主要角色✦】</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🌿 莉潔特｜精靈少女</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3830690/extras/a5d3fa0e909fc3bc1fb13f08b16fdf0f.poster.avif?t=1776391686\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3830690/extras/a5d3fa0e909fc3bc1fb13f08b16fdf0f.webm?t=1776391686\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\