6391686\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>嚮往戶外世界、為追尋自由而踏上旅途的精靈少女。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >然而才剛享受到自由的空氣，便被不懷好意的人類囚禁，在過程中為你所救。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >透過這次的逃難過程，因緣際會之下從你身上學習到如何生存與戰鬥。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >自由奔放的她，將在與你的羈絆中逐漸成長，也被你所吸引......</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🪄 希爾薇亞｜魔女<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3830690/extras/9fad8ff709ac1ebb16d0b4b752e1c4e7.poster.avif?t=1776391686\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3830690/extras/9fad8ff709ac1ebb16d0b4b752e1c4e7.webm?t=1776391686\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3830690/extras/9fad8ff709ac1ebb16d0b4b752e1c4e7.mp4?t=1776391686\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >擁有悠久歲月的次元魔女，個性狡黠且神秘。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >她與你維持著長期的合作關係，她的出現，會為這段旅途帶來怎樣的波瀾呢？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🌸 艾菈｜祭司<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3830690/extras/894b8dfeb8e8fd59f411e80b015149c7.poster.avif?t=1776391686\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3830690/extras/894b8dfeb8e8fd59f411e80b015149c7.webm?t=1776391686\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3830690/extras/894b8dfeb8e8fd59f411e80b015149c7.mp4?t=1776391686\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >祭司，過去一同冒險過的同伴。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >過去曾經猛烈的追求過你，但因為其有問題的性格而沒被你接受。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在這次旅途中，你將與特殊的方式跟她再續前緣......</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>", "short_description": "身為忍者的你在旅途中救下了精靈少女莉潔特。 在逃亡與修行的生活中，培養感情、育成角色，展開一段充滿親密互動的浪漫喜劇之旅！", "supported_languages": "繁體中文, 英文, 日文<strong>*</strong>, 簡體中文, 韓文<br><strong>*</strong>具備完整音效支援的語言", "header_image": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3830690/6d5c8b6d6c036f5e9549a45d91b7065076bf5add/header_tchinese.jpg?t=1776391686", "capsule_image": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3830690/1abf17b9cca3e85bc08ec0142ed44f12ee63c2bc/capsule_231x87_tchinese.jpg?t=1776391686", "capsule_imagev5": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3830690/1abf17b9cca3e85bc08ec0142ed44f12ee63c2bc/capsule_184x69_tchinese.jpg?t=1776391686", "website": null, "pc_requirements": {"minimum": "<strong>最低配備:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>作業系統:</strong> Windows 10<br></li><li><strong>處理器:</strong> Intel Core i5 7th gen<br></li><li><strong>記憶體:</strong> 6 GB 記憶體<br></li><li><strong>顯示卡:</strong> NIVDIA GeForce GTX 1060<br></li><li><strong>DirectX:</strong> 版本：12<br></li><li><strong>儲存空間:</strong> 6 GB 可用空間</li></ul>"}, "mac_requirements": [], "linux_requirements": [], "developers": ["Barance Studio"], "publishers": ["Mango Party", " Mango Party News"], "price_overview": {"currency": "TWD", "initial": 29900, "final": 26900, "discount_percent": 10, "initial_formatted": "NT$ 299", "final_formatted": "NT$ 269"}, "categories": [{"id": 2, "description": "單人"}, {"id": 22, "description": "Steam 成就"}, {"id": 23, "description": "Steam 雲端"}, {"id": 62, "description": "親友同享"}], "genres": [{"id": "3", "description": "角色扮演"}, {"id": "28", "description": "模擬"}], "release_date": {"coming_soon": false, "date": "2026 年 4 月 16 日"}}}}, "us": {"3830690": {"success": true, "data": {"type": "game", "name": "Flee, My Elven Ninja!  3D", "steam_appid": 3830690, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "dlc": [4207150, 4209540], "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3830690/extras/f9817c32b06f0e3266608b630955250b.poster.avif?t=1776391686\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3830690/extras/f9817c32b06f0e3266608b630955250b.webm?t=1776391686\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3830690/extras/f9817c32b06f0e3266608b630955250b.mp4?t=1776391686\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>💖 Escape × Romance × Training — Embark on a unique, heartfelt journey with an elven maiden! </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3830690/extras/f56a17355b80edd34df4b29248418a6b.avif?t=1776391686\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3830690/extras_big/f56a17355b80edd34df4b29248418a6b.webp?t=1776391686 width=1560 height=877 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >【✦Introduction✦】</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >WA-TA! You're a badass ninja. And, as fate would have it, your latest mission is to save an elven maiden that's been imprisoned, Lizet. But the world is a dangerous place, so to ensure her survival, you decide to train her in the ways of ninjutsu.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3830690/extras/51f52ad8447c9cca0d31e87a2417eab2.avif?t=1776391686\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3830690/extras_big/51f52ad8447c9cca0d31e87a2417eab2.webp?t=1776391686 width=1560 height=877 /></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As you flee from the kingdom and train her as your disciple, your relationship with her begins to quietly change...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >What began as an honest relationship between master and disciple has slowly grown into something deeper. As you and Lizet interact on a regular basis, and spend more time together, perhaps...something might happen that will make both of your hearts race?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3830690/extras/8e9926121452379332790db90ebe7965.avif?t=1776391686\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3830690/extras_big/8e9926121452379332790db90ebe7965.webp?t=1776391686 width=1560 height=877 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is an adult simulation game that features character cultivation, daily interactions, and optional intimate moments. Get ready for an exciting romantic comedy that takes place while living on the run.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >【✦Core Gameplay: Adventure, Life, and Daily Moments with Her✦】</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3830690/extras/f47fa8bdee82253a1a6718265a4fcbf3.avif?t=1776391686\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3830690/extras_big/f47fa8bdee82253a1a6718265a4fcbf3.webp?t=1776391686 width=1560 height=877 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >[Sandbox Nurturing]: Spend time in your private hideout. From the cozy dining table to the intimate bed, close the distance between your hearts step by step.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3830690/extras/35f8aa7e9faa67b1a17d421f99e42431.avif?t=1776391686\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3830690/extras_big/35f8aa7e9faa67b1a17d421f99e42431.webp?t=1776391686 width=1560 height=877 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >[Resource Gathering]: Forage for food when hungry; hunt monsters when short on crystals. Survive, thrive, and become &quot;stronger&quot; than ever.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3830690/extras/5e753afea918c4b85fc767e228eb48b0.avif?t=1776391686\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3830690/extras_big/5e753afea918c4b85fc767e228eb48b0.webp?t=1776391686 width=1560 height=877 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >[Turn-Based Strategy]: A classic, intuitive combat system. Watch Lizet showcase her heroic grace on the battlefield!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3830690/extras/a2b3b404dc3a128c41ead42421c81520.avif?t=1776391686\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3830690/extras_big/a2b3b404dc3a128c41ead42421c81520.webp?t=1776391686 width=1560 height=877 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >[Ultimate Relaxation]: Exhausted from training? Return to the lounge for various &quot;Interaction Modes&quot; and let the stress melt away amidst heavy breathing.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3830690/extras/2c399f321bedd23099a97516e95362c8.avif?t=1776391686\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3830690/extras_big/2c399f321bedd23099a97516e95362c8.webp?t=1776391686 width=1560 height=877 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >【✦Premium Sensory Feast: The Ultimate Immersive Experience✦】</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✨ Full Japanese voice acting for female characters to enhance their charm and make the experience fully immersive!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✨ Full 3D cartoon rendering that makes for super duper sensory overload!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✨ 360° camera control for the intimate scenes. Check out every single detail of her body and movements! ✨</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✨ Over 29 animated intimate scenes~♥</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✨ 3 different endings! You choose how the future unfolds!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3830690/extras/d040a3f165eb32149811acabd28b2009.avif?t=1776391686\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3830690/extras_big/d040a3f165eb32149811acabd28b2009.webp?t=1776391686 width=1560 height=877 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >【✦Main Characters✦】</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🌿 Lizet | Elven Girl</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3830690/extras/f8f7bd5688dbde1d1569240a238fba7c.poster.avif?t=1776391686\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3830690/extras/f8f7bd5688dbde1d1569240a238fba7c.webm?t=1776391686\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3830690/extras/f8f7bd5688dbde1d1569240a238fba7c.mp4?t=1776391686\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >An elven maiden who longs for the outside world and sets off in search of freedom.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Just as she gets a whiff of what she so desires, some no-good, ill-intended humans capture her! Luckily, you show up just in time to save her...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As you two flee for your lives, you teach her how to fight and survive.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The bond between you grows, and so does Lizet's free spirit. As time passes, she finds herself becoming attracted to her master...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🪄Sylva | Witch</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3830690/extras/cb4f5380637e6145c47dd260442680cf.poster.avif?t=1776391686\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3830690/extras/cb4f5380637e6145c47dd260442680cf.webm?t=1776391686\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3830690/extras/cb4f5380637e6145c47dd260442680cf.mp4?t=1776391686\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A witch skilled in dimensional magic, who is as old as she is mysterious...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Silva has been working with you for quite some time, though it's unclear whether she's here to help you with this journey...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🌸 Ayla | Priestess</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3830690/extras/295d2b216d724dcd4261d17a358de3f2.poster.avif?t=1776391686\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3830690/extras/295d2b216d724dcd4261d17a358de3f2.webm?t=1776391686\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3830690/extras/295d2b216d724dcd4261d17a358de3f2.mp4?t=1776391686\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A member of your former adventuring party, and a highly skilled priestess.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >At one point in time, she was actively pursuing you as a romantic partner. However, her...unique personality made it difficult for you to feel the same way.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >And yet fate has deemed it fit for you two to meet again, albeit in a rather unusual way...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>", "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3830690/extras/f9817c32b06f0e3266608b630955250b.poster.avif?t=1776391686\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3830690/extras/f9817c32b06f0e3266608b630955250b.webm?t=1776391686\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3830690/extras/f9817c32b06f0e3266608b630955250b.mp4?t=1776391686\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>💖 Escape × Romance × Training — Embark on a unique, heartfelt journey with an elven maiden! </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3830690/extras/f56a17355b80edd34df4b29248418a6b.avif?t=1776391686\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3830690/extras_big/f56a17355b80edd34df4b29248418a6b.webp?t=1776391686 width=1560 height=877 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >【✦Introduction✦】</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >WA-TA! You're a badass ninja. And, as fate would have it, your latest mission is to save an elven maiden that's been imprisoned, Lizet. But the world is a dangerous place, so to ensure her survival, you decide to train her in the ways of ninjutsu.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3830690/extras/51f52ad8447c9cca0d31e87a2417eab2.avif?t=1776391686\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3830690/extras_big/51f52ad8447c9cca0d31e87a2417eab2.webp?t=1776391686 width=1560 height=877 /></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As you flee from the kingdom and train her as your disciple, your relationship with her begins to quietly change...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >What began as an honest relationship between master and disciple has slowly grown into something deeper. As you and Lizet interact on a regular basis, and spend more time together, perhaps...something might happen that will make both of your hearts race?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3830690/extras/8e9926121452379332790db90ebe7965.avif?t=1776391686\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3830690/extras_big/8e9926121452379332790db90ebe7965.webp?t=1776391686 width=1560 height=877 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is an adult simulation game that features character cultivation, daily interactions, and optional intimate moments. Get ready for an exciting romantic comedy that takes place while living on the run.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >【✦Core Gameplay: Adventure, Life, and Daily Moments with Her✦】</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3830690/extras/f47fa8bdee82253a1a6718265a4fcbf3.avif?t=1776391686\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3830690/extras_big/f47fa8bdee82253a1a6718265a4fcbf3.webp?t=1776391686 width=1560 height=877 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >[Sandbox Nurturing]: Spend time in your private hideout. From the cozy dining table to the intimate bed, close the distance between your hearts step by step.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3830690/extras/35f8aa7e9faa67b1a17d421f99e42431.avif?t=1776391686\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3830690/extras_big/35f8aa7e9faa67b1a17d421f99e42431.webp?t=1776391686 width=1560 height=877 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >[Resource Gathering]: Forage for food when hungry; hunt monsters when short on crystals. Survive, thrive, and become &quot;stronger&quot; than ever.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3830690/extras/5e753afea918c4b85fc767e228eb48b0.avif?t=1776391686\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3830690/extras_big/5e753afea918c4b85fc767e228eb48b0.webp?t=1776391686 width=1560 height=877 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >[Turn-Based Strategy]: A classic, intuitive combat system. Watch Lizet showcase her heroic grace on the battlefield!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3830690/extras/a2b3b404dc3a128c41ead42421c81520.avif?t=1776391686\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3830690/extras_big/a2b3b404dc3a128c41ead42421c81520.webp?t=1776391686 width=1560 height=877 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >[Ultimate Relaxation]: Exhausted from training? Return to the lounge for various &quot;Interaction Modes&quot; and let the stress melt away amidst heavy breathing.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3830690/extras/2c399f321bedd23099a97516e95362c8.avif?t=1776391686\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3830690/extras_big/2c399f321bedd23099a97516e95362c8.webp?t=1776391686 width=1560 height=877 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >【✦Premium Sensory Feast: The Ultimate Immersive Experience✦】</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✨ Full Japanese voice acting for female characters to enhance their charm and make the experience fully 